      "description": "Hey everyone! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream! This car has been babied since day one and looks like it just rolled right off the showroom floor. Not a single scratch to be found, the interior is totally spotless, and it drives just as smooth as the day I got it. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019m super happy to chat and show you around!",
