    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a meticulously preserved E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit boasts a verified subframe reinforcement and documented rod bearing service, addressing the platform's primary mechanical concerns. The S54\u2019s individual throttle bodies provide instantaneous response, while the Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox delivers precise gate entry. The exterior retains its factory luster with consistent paint depth across all panels, and the interior bolsters show negligible wear. Mechanically, the VANOS system has been overhauled to ensure optimal variable valve timing. Riding on a refreshed suspension with OEM bushings, this chassis remains exceptionally taut, offering the pure analog feedback expected from a flagship M-division product.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
