      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-quality specimen that satisfies the most discerning collector. This vehicle has been exclusively garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen inclement weather. The exterior paint retains a deep, glass-like luster entirely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather is supple with no creasing, and the interior still possesses that distinct new-car aroma. Every mechanical system performs flawlessly, backed by a comprehensive, paper-trail service history from authorized specialists. The undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork, and the wheels are pristine with no curb rash. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did on the showroom floor.",
